{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"a2edadacc4","title":"关于审阅黄炎培在上海工商界的讲话稿的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"78d5e75be5","index":0,"year":1954,"month":3,"day":12,"articleId":"a2edadacc4"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"id":"e23dcf99fa","name":"发言","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji34","name":"毛泽东全集第34卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/34-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji34":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"4ecf897e93","type":"title","text":"关于审阅黄炎培！在上海工商界的讲话稿的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"a2edadacc4"},{"id":"6800fc9b83","type":"paragraph","text":"黄副总理：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"a2edadacc4"},{"id":"bccb5a7e11","type":"paragraph","text":"三月八日惠书阅悉。附件已付周总理季维汉部长翻药奉告。“人们”是指资产阶级和民主党派，不包括地主阶级和管资产阶级，即不是“包括一切的”。“无痛分婉法”一词最好不写在印刷品上，因实际上那些不甚觉悟的人们总会觉得有些痛苦的。支票开得多了，可能引起幻想，而不去加重教育和学习，不去提高政治觉悟，结果感觉痛苦的人就会对我们不满。尚请的。敬颂大安","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"a2edadacc4"},{"id":"390e0fb417","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"a2edadacc4"},{"id":"f278de8030","type":"paragraph","text":"一九五四年三月十二日于杭州","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"a2edadacc4"},{"id":"692bcb0e5a","type":"paragraph","text":"黄炎培，当时任中国民主建国会主任委员、政务院副总理。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"a2edadacc4"},{"id":"59b19a7d1e","type":"paragraph","text":"2]指黄炎培1954年3月1日对上海工商界的讲话福。","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"a2edadacc4"},{"id":"ac12bce5c8","type":"paragraph","text":"李维汉，当时任中共中央统战部部长。","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"a2edadacc4"},{"id":"16edac98bc","type":"paragraph","text":"一恩来、维汉同志：","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"a2edadacc4"},{"id":"32906b56b9","type":"paragraph","text":"此件请审阅割的，并告黄副总理。“阶级消灭，个人愉快”似以改为“阶级消灭，个人存在”为适宜，亦可告以非正式发表的谈话不要他在印刷品中引用，请的。如他的讲演不登报，又碍难修改，听其引用亦无不可。他所谓“无痛分婉法”亦不甚妥当，只作印刷品不登报，亦可不改。未了引我的话之后他说“人们”“是包括一切的”，我已复告他不是包括一切的，地主阶级和管资产阶级不包括在内。我复黄信只说这一点和批评无痛分婉法一点，此外说他的信已付你们二位封的告他。","index":9,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"a2edadacc4"},{"id":"b54043e38d","type":"paragraph","text":"敬礼！","index":10,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"a2edadacc4"},{"id":"a27b79cf11","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":11,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"a2edadacc4"},{"id":"d0fa00b016","type":"paragraph","text":"一九五四年三月十二日","index":12,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"a2edadacc4"},{"id":"2df5cd8bb2","type":"paragraph","text":"复黄信请阅后送交。","index":13,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"a2edadacc4"}],"page":{"id":"9c3c2051cd","publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"a2edadacc4","start":46,"end":47}}}},"__N_SSG":true}